Don't expect much...this is a low end hotel. Everything in room was clean albeit very old. Nice to have a full fridge and kitchen esp for a stay of more than a night or two.  Customer service was decent, friendly. Excellent location if you want to be off strip but not too far. Easy walk to Monorail. Overall, not bad...not great.

