f-kw2D40Kzq8mlS8Td7rhw
My first experience with a Vegas nightclub and I was amazed! Beautiful decor, beautiful staff, incredible, immersive sound system. The moving chandelier was so cool and the dancers and acrobats added a definite Vegas flair to the whole evening. Drinks (even water) were incredibly expensive so I did not partake but I had a blast listening to the djs, dancing, and watching people party. The table service seemed like the way to go if you had the bucks to spend. I prebought tickets so there was really not much of a line to get in although it was a bit of a cluster trying to figure out where to go. I would def recommend this if you are attending a big show....there was no way some of those people in that loooong line were getting in.

